items.title: San Franciscans who test positive for COVID-19 and are at high risk for severe illness are eligible for COVID medicines
items.summary: San Franciscans can be prepared for COVID-19 by knowing if they, or someone they love, are at high risk for severe illness and how to get COVID-19 medicines.

items.title: SF ramps up mobile COVID-19 testing to target resources to hardest hit communities
items.summary: The new mobile testing vans are part of a strategy to be able to rapidly expand or contract testing as needed as the high-capacity 7th and Brannan test site closes on March 31.
